(512, 38, '2017-06-22 04:57:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Responsible to organize all the logistical administration and process, to include communication, scheduling and other operations as necessary for logistic procedure\r\nResponsible for ensuring project procurement files are kept up-to-date\r\nResponsible to establish and maintain good contact with suppliers, government offices, banks and other agencies with regards to logistic matters\r\nResponsible for performing all necessary activities from LC Opening to LC Settlement ( Check Proforma Invoice &amp; fill up LC form)\r\nLogistic Officers must also track shipments to ensure they arrive on time and that shipment and delivery processes adhere to any pertinent regulations\r\nWork closely with concern department and carry out advance Payment through TT, Settlement of Bi.Bi.Ni. form and released credit payment via Pragyapan Patra\r\nPreparing port document: Kolkata/ Haldia for LC/TT Consignment released and LC Status Maintenance\r\nResponsible for Usance LC Payment Scheduling and Freight Payment\r\nAny other responsibilities may be directed by the Logistic Manager and HOD', 'Sarbottam Cement P. Ltd. A unit of Saurabh Group is Nepal\'s first European Plant with VRM Technology, the most advanced technology humans have innovated till date globally for quality cement manufacturing. The Plant is located at the prime industrial location of Parasi, Nepal strengthening it further to spread its network in all parts of the country. The plant is one of its kind moulded with Green Technology from Denmark.', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2017-06-22 04:57:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://ourjobdesk.com/?p=512', 0, 'post', '', 0);
