(513, 39, '2017-06-22 05:16:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'East West Engineering Service Pvt. Ltd. (EWES) is a leading national consulting company having competent multidisciplinary design and construction management team.\r\nEWES goal is to provide professional services and create safe and functional built form. It aims to deliver high quality design and ethical construction management services to the\r\nclient. EWES intends to hire professionally sound and dynamic technical personnel, having firm faith and confidence, committed to work with our team at central office, Kathmandu\r\nand for Emergency School Reconstruction Project (ESRP) in earthquake affected Districts viz. Gorkha, Dhading, Rasuwa, lalitpur, Makawanpur and Nuwakot of Nepal in the\r\nfollowing positions.\r\n\r\n\r\nJob Specifications:\r\n\r\n\r\nShall have management leadership and corporate culture promoting qualities\r\nMust have high level of analytical skills, capable of quickly sensing the interests of stakeholders and acting upon accordingly. Proficient in report writing both in Nepali and\r\nEnglish\r\nShould not be convicted on any heinous crime\r\nShall be recognized from his/her past performances\r\nMust have good coordination/communication skills\r\nShall be familiar with Auto Cad, Excel, Word and MS Project', 'District Resident Engineers', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2017-06-22 05:16:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://ourjobdesk.com/?p=513', 0, 'post', '', 0);
